<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="c878f978-3c35-4576-94f8-267012c3e76a" >

    <h2><a id="about"></a>About</h2> 
<p>The in-page accessibility checker will instantly check your page for accessibility and usability issues when enabled. The tool checks for content issues such as images missing alternative text, non-descriptive&nbsp;hyperlinks, poor heading structure, incorrect use of components and much more. </p> 
<p>Errors or warnings will be indicated exactly before or after where the issue is detected. The error message will be displayed in a convenient tooltip on how to fix.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#c878f978-3c35-4576-94f8-267012c3e76a");});</script></div>

